          good to be True?
        %p.trust_issues_txt It's okay we have trust issues as well!
      .photo_evidence    
        %img{:src => "#{@shwag_winner_looser_popup.real.url(:medium)}"}/         
      %p.enough_shot 
        If the photo isn't enough shoot us an email
        %p.russ_email
          %a{:href => "#"} russ@thestashbox.com
